            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>spinach </strong>and pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Dissolve your<strong> pho broth paste </strong>in 600ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[750ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[900ml] </span><strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>stock</strong></p><p>Reboil a kettle</p>",
      "order": 3,
